### Health check
GET http://localhost:8080/health

### List lessons
GET http://localhost:8080/api/lessons

### Login
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{"login":"admin","password":"admin2026"}

### Create lesson
POST http://localhost:8080/api/lessons
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "language": "English",
  "level": "B1",
  "title": "Travel small talk",
  "duration": "20 min",
  "goal": "Practice short dialogues for travel situations"
}

### Metrics
GET http://localhost:8080/api/metrics
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Delete lesson
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/lessons/lesson-id
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
